{"tid":175041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（一不離二）調景嶺都會駅商場扶手梯冒煙","createTime":"2017-03-27T08:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T14:26:30.000Z","uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a00e564bc18a620ed00d251bf10cc331f0cca816","tid":175041,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T08:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170327/large/1490601757_15a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170327%2Flarge%2F1490601757_15a4.jpg&h=9f085d23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5231a290021ea7a7186b7d733cf53a619ce5932","tid":175041,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T08:40:14.000Z","msg":"朗豪坊扶手梯發生溜後事件第三天，另一商場的扶手梯又有事故。調景嶺站B出口，連接都會駅商場地下至一樓的一條扶手梯，下午突然冒煙。<br />\n<br />\n讀者張先生稱大約下午3時20分經過現場時，行人還可以沿扶手梯上落，但10分鐘後折返，卻見扶手梯冒出白煙，並且往港鐵站及一樓商場擴散。現場聞到一陣濃烈燶味，氣味飄出巴士站，管理處職員見狀隨即用圍板封住扶手梯上落位，並疏散現場市民遠離梯邊。"},{"pid":"4aea26356e44cf98dbc6129607f71aff93d3530c","tid":175041,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T08:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27522667377a983552cab79a97bbb367bffc6b4","tid":175041,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T08:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96242115e3b6384fbb557f774c91b31027e4d111","tid":175041,"uid":15211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:48:54.000Z","msg":"藍田都出事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325ec792dc082aa404d0ce5968c5cc29f8482741","tid":175041,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:51:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55155dc99818b4d52c3684b0266bb9700af666e2","tid":175041,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"